{
  "texts": [
    "For tools developed by creators from multiple countries, contributions are evenly distributed across all represented geographies (i.e.",
    "a tool with author institutions from n countries contributes 1/n to each country's total).",
    "Source: RAND and CLTR analysis 2025 In total, 235 small biomolecule design tools originated from 51 countries in the full dataset (including tools assigned to multiple categories).",
    "The numbers in circles indicate the locations of the finalist small biomolecule design tools.",
    "The six finalist tools came from nine countries: China, Canada, India, Austria, Italy, Netherlands, Switzerland, United Kingdom and United States of America."
  ]
}